      <title>国债拍卖创纪录之前下跌； NYCB 飙升：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票期货上涨，债券下跌，随后 10 年期国债抛售规模达到创纪录的 420 亿美元，投资者也在等待美联储几位发言人就利率走势提供线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 22:55:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
